        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&REPLY_ID=67174&TOPIC_ID=3496&FORUM_ID=53&CAT_ID=1&Forum_Title=Necromancer+Game+Guides&Topic_Title=Howling+Stones+Solo&M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height=15 width=15 alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>


        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">A few key points.</P><P>I did HS without an epic...so I could not do all the spawns in the entry in one cycle.  However, I had a druid friend with epic and we did the entry together.  It was slower exp, but much funner to have someone along for the ride.</P><P>An Undead Oblation can dispell you.  I had that happen and he got my DMF off...that sucked.</P><P>Keep your HP above 40%.  Most of the times I have had things aggro me was when my HP dipped below 40%.  You can get stuff come from below if you let your HP go below 40%.</P><P>I recommend spending as little time in the middle, sunken area, as possible.  Things tend to aggro from below if you are sitting in there.</P><P>The East Wing roamer mob can be avoided by avoiding that section of the platform.  Just never go to the East section of the platform except to loot.  I had one Druid who did not get this.  He kept backing up into the East section of the area and we kept getting mobs randomly aggroed onto to us.  Another druid I was with paid attention and never went to the East side of the platform.  We hardly ever aggroed anything...meaning we would go for days without any funky aggro.</P><P>Do not tempt that roaming mob at the East Wing that is over 50th level.  It will summon you and take you down fast.  You can charm it..and it rips things up.  But when charm breaks..you are next.  LOL!</P><P>And the South entrance is the one with the banner over the door.</P><P>Exp in this location is good up to and including 60..thanks to the new light blue exp code.</P><P>Ishtarra Gemeinseele<BR>Warlock of Tunare</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

