        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I first gave this a try last night.  When I zoned in the sepulcher aggro'd me but i had skin up and was able to charm him.  I killed him, the other roamer and a golem just to see how things went then I had to gate out and log.  I thought it was very nice exp and I will be headed back there tonight =)<BR>As far as how to deal with the sepulcher repop, could you just invis vs undead when you are getting ready for repop?  That would give you enough time to root and darkness him...you will take a HT but thats no problem as long as he isnt meleeing you as well.  The invis should give you the opportunity to move away from him if he pops on top of ya without having to deal with HT + melee. Just trying to find an alternative to having skin up for the roamer repop like the last post =).  Any suggestions?</P><P><BR>Alizouran Anamun<BR>55 Necro<BR>Inny</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
