        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Well zoning in you should feign death the instant you get in.  I usually spam hit Alt+8(or whichever spell slot feign is in) so when I actually zone in I'll already be on my way to getting feign off.  If you are already inside, I usually hit my circlet and go sit on a staircase until repop.  I used to let both repop, charm one and kill the other, but then I just started to eat the HT and vex it back.  I can usually get all 8 golems in one round ... but then again I have epic and demilich. :)</P><P>And you want to watch out for the undertaker skelly.  Sometimes I'll be killing a golem and all of a sudden I eat a 750ish HT.  I don't know how he aggros, but I suspect it may have something to do with him roaming into the portal down below.</P><P><center><BR><img src="http://brad.clan-rum.org/rhaiqtag.jpg"></P><P>"Amputate a man's leg and he can still feel it tickling.  Tell me mom, when your little girl is on the slab, where will it tickle you?"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
